{"tid":1664080,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍心報名參選西營盤 稱要「保護中聯辦」 提名不足衝閘失敗","createTime":"2019-10-19T22:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T01:49:44.000Z","uid":1886,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e71896519271f6c74fd76441bf9cfa5de9677091","tid":1664080,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T22:51:33.000Z","msg":"區議會選舉提名期近日結束，網絡紅人「龍心」報名參選中西區「西營盤」選區，稱要「保護中聯辦」。不過，龍心所獲的11票提名中，有5票被裁定無效，提名人並非當區選民，最終入閘失敗。他指僅用一日時間在街上收集提名，感到難過但已盡力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w274/public/column_images/10172.jpg?itok=0F_p7zY0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw274%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F10172.jpg%3Fitok%3D0F_p7zY0&h=ca926c9c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n龍心報名時表示，參選是希望展示潛能，又指區議會是第一步，第二步是立法會，第三步是「民間特首」或「臨時大總統」，有信心解決「黃藍之間的爭鬥」，平衡雙方糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067998\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067998&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=0635f6ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1067998&h=08b50c61\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1067998</a>"},{"pid":"26171a1e8bf6e60ba17a66c7bd23d348fabab1e4","tid":1664080,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T22:51:39.000Z","msg":"[創意抗爭] 網民尖沙咀辦「警暴展覽」稱為喚起國際關注<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eotKoS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eotKoS</a>"},{"pid":"2158b710fba4b9ccd29a566e1fd50fc206bae278","tid":1664080,"uid":1886,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T22:52:14.000Z","msg":"龍心指選擇西營盤選區，因為要「保護中聯辦」，他指中聯辦及國家絕不能被侮辱，現時香港的問題「聰明的人都知道，是大英政府遺留落嚟嘅炸彈，唔關共產黨事」。<br />\n<br />\n龍心表明支持中國，稱要將英國留下來的法治連根拔起，令香港「再成為中國人的火車頭」。他又指不應乞求美國幫助，形容是「搵個殺父仇人，搵返嚟欺凌你阿媽」。<br />\n<br />\n但他又指，希望西營盤要有西方文化，要提升區內教育水平，並稱自己肯定能勝出，因為沒有人夠膽保護中聯辦。他又稱主張通過「隻揪合法化」，「快快趣解決鬥爭問題」。"},{"pid":"71a353b7466919bad6f912bfa8021676faddb36c","tid":1664080,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T22:52:47.000Z","msg":"不過選舉主任最終裁定他所獲的11票提名中，有5票無效，提名人並非當區選民。龍心坦言感到難過，但指自己用一日時間在區內收集提名，已經盡了最大努力。他表示未來有機會舉辦遊行集會，「希望政府可以見到我嘅能力請我啦」，其後便帶著他今日用作收集提名的電動滑板車離去。"},{"pid":"48aa566ef31b24938dbe7841e8105ae87daf3d68","tid":1664080,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T22:53:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CehHAt2s3Vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCehHAt2s3Vk&d=kavsisi6QTOS4EBqYfxwc0XxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=7e86663b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CehHAt2s3Vk</a>"},{"pid":"9545c0ef6dba5d99d3de7b9f4521f41720dca687","tid":1664080,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:11:42.000Z","msg":"條友真係唔對路"},{"pid":"afe297ffb57b36b790310e8dbd6e1f12f72f56fc","tid":1664080,"uid":35924,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:41:47.000Z","msg":"隻揪合法化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑到仆街"},{"pid":"014438800a5e1ac453606d46b303bde233b76f03","tid":1664080,"uid":60279,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:46:54.000Z","msg":"電動滑板車<br />\n犯法重叫政府請你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條友痴線到咁樣"},{"pid":"19fca85eba060aedaa9ecb1d4d56636df067e6c6","tid":1664080,"uid":128748,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T23:50:19.000Z","msg":"好想投票比佢，點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec5c6a0c18745d7d32ce459c848f78f08d112491","tid":1664080,"uid":65187,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9545c0ef